sources.title: Code of the Fearless (1939) FRED SCOTT
sources.description:
Stars: Fred Scott, Claire Rochelle, John Merton
Director: Bernard B. Ray

A Texas Ranger infiltrates a gang of ruthless bandits at their secret hideout, but his identity is revealed when a message to his Captain is intercepted!

metadata.Plot: When it appears that Fred Jamison is a member of Red's gang, he is kicked out of the Rangers. But it's just a plot between Fred and the Ranger Captain. Fred then gets into Red's gang and makes plans that will enable the Rangers to bring them all in. But his message to the Captain is intercepted and the hoax revealed.
